  m_text: This will let you choose if the bots are visible or not. Great for practicing
    the mechanic without relaying on them for your own position.<br><br>- <b>Hide
    Characters</b> means that only the nameplate and model of the bots are hidden.<br><br>-
    <b>Completely Hidden</b> means that everything regarding the bots are hidden,
    no tether visuals, no debuff visuals, nothing. This setting can make some timelines
    incredibly difficult or impossible to do.
